--font-family-vault.light: Arlrdbd, "Source Han Sans", "Noto Sans CJK", "Source Sans Pro"

background-image.light:
repeating-linear-gradient(
      45deg,
      hsla(0, 0%, 100%, 0.3),
      hsla(0, 0%, 100%, 0.3) 20px,
      transparent 0,
      transparent 60px
    ),
    repeating-linear-gradient(
      -45deg,
      hsla(0, 0%, 100%, 0.3),
      hsla(0, 0%, 100%, 0.3) 20px,
      transparent 0,
      transparent 60px
    )

repeating-linear-gradient(
      45deg,
      hsla(0, 0%, 100%, 0.3),
      hsla(0, 0%, 100%, 0.3) 20px,
      transparent 0,
      transparent 60px
    ),
    repeating-linear-gradient(
      -45deg,
      hsla(0, 0%, 100%, 0.3),
      hsla(0, 0%, 100%, 0.3) 20px,
      transparent 0,
      transparent 60px
    )
